Subject: [PATCH 2/6] =?UTF-8?q?fix(report=5Fcarbone):=20stateless=20carbon?=
 =?UTF-8?q?e-ee=20=E2=80=94=20geen=20/templates-endpoint?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

get_extension_file_from_api gebruikt /templates (search/versioning) → bestaat
niet in stateless mode (error-string code w130) → res.get() AttributeError bij
template-ID-zetten. Nu default .docx als res geen dict is.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 report_carbone/models/base/ir_actions_report.py | 8 +++++++-
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/report_carbone/models/base/ir_actions_report.py b/report_carbone/models/base/ir_actions_report.py
index 9452e63..57c3aa1 100644
--- a/report_carbone/models/base/ir_actions_report.py
+++ b/report_carbone/models/base/ir_actions_report.py
@@ -859,9 +859,15 @@ class IrActionsReportCarbone(models.Model):
         }
         res = self.call_carbone_endpoint(endpoint, params, raise_error)
 
+        # BB Open patch: on-premise carbone-ee draait stateless (geen DB) → het
+        # /templates-endpoint bestaat niet (error-string, code w130) i.p.v. een
+        # JSON-dict. Default dan naar .docx (WAF-templates zijn .docx).
+        if not isinstance(res, dict):
+            return ".docx"
+
         data_list = res.get("data")
         if not data_list:
-            return False
+            return ".docx"
 
         return data_list[0].get("type")
 
